Ok...when you cast AE mez on someone who is below the damage limit of mez, it doesn't spread to other people.  This is very annoying.<P>I assumed this was a bug...but someone this week told me that Mythic actually intends it to be this way.  Is this true?<P>It's an area effect spell...why does it rely on specific target to determine if it spreads?  It should cover the area no matter what.<P>Also, I havn't tested this...but say you target someone who has already been Str/Con debuffed.  If you cast Str/Con ae debuff again, will it still spread?<P>--------------------<P>Englebertius<BR>Sorc - Iseult
